<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="blue-adj">blue <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bluː/    美 /bluː/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>蓝色的；蔚蓝的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sky is deep blue. 
天空湛蓝。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His face was <strong>blue with cold</strong>. 
他脸冻得发青。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>悲伤的；沮丧的；忧郁的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m <strong>feeling</strong> rather <strong>blue</strong> today. 
我今天心情很差。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="black-and-blue">black and blue</h3>
<p>1.<strong>被打得青一块紫一块的；伤痕累累的</strong>  </p></div>